room_title: Escape room "Lab Rats" by 15 Locks in Austin
room_address: 2113 Wells Branch Pkwy Suite 4300 Austin, TX 78728
room_description: You have volunteered yourself for a human psychological experiment. Like rats in a maze, your team must find ways to communicate efficiently and solve colorful puzzles across three different rooms using teamwork and communication skills. Only by working together and listening to each other will your team manage to get your rat to its cheese and open that final success door!
